%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Top%20economist%20Mark%20Zandi%20says%20Trump%20has%20a%20week%20to%20strike%20an%20Iran%20deal%20before%20the%20US%20faces%20a%20'real%20problem'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22President%20Donald%20Trump%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1d77052e5a80cfe0501be6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKent%20NISHIMURA%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMark%20Zandi%20thinks%20Trump%20has%20about%20a%20week%20to%20strike%20an%20Iran%20deal%20before%20the%20US%20has%20bigger%20problems.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAbsent%20a%20peace%20deal%2C%20oil%20prices%20could%20soar%20again%2C%20triggering%20a%20US%20recession%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOther%20forecasters%20have%20warned%20that%20it%20won't%20be%20long%20before%20economic%20damage%20from%20the%20war%20is%20more%20visible.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20halting%20peace%20negotiations%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Iran%20need%20to%20result%20in%20a%20deal%20soon%20if%20the%20US%20is%20going%20to%20avoid%20deeper%20economic%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20according%20to%20Moody's%20top%20economist%20Mark%20Zandi%2C%20who%20said%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20about%20a%20week%20to%20secure%20a%20peace%20deal%20before%20the%20effects%20of%20the%20war%20make%20it%20more%20likely%20that%20the%20economy%20will%20fall%20into%20a%20recession.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%20on%20Monday%2C%20Iran%20has%20said%20that%20it%20will%20cease%20negotiations%20and%20block%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20until%20key%20demands%20are%20met.%20That's%20bad%20news%20for%20Trump%2C%20who%20has%20teased%20a%20deal%20for%20weeks%20with%20nothing%20concrete%20to%20show%20for%20it.%20Oil%20spiked%20on%20Monday%20morning%2C%20with%20Brent%20and%20US%20crude%20prices%20rising%20by%20about%207%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FhTmF5%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Brent%20crude%20prices%20year-to-date%2C%20in%20dollars%20per%20barrel%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22442%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EZandi%20said%20at%20the%20end%20of%20last%20week%20that%20the%20ongoing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-market-supply-shortage-outlook-iran-war-crude-inventories-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esurge%20in%20oil%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20have%20a%20more%20meaningful%20impact%20on%20consumers%20and%20the%20economy%20if%20they%20do%20not%20come%20back%20down%20in%20the%20next%20week.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spike%20in%20crude%20has%20already%20pushed%20the%20US%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-recession-warning-job-market-signal-unemploymen-trate-mark-zandi-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprecipice%20of%20a%20recession%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20hope%20is%20that%20a%20peace%20deal%20could%20cool%20oil%20prices%20enough%20to%20take%20the%20US%20from%20the%20critical%20threshold%20that%20could%20spark%20a%20downturn%2C%20Zandi%20said%2C%20speaking%20to%20Bloomberg%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20gotta%20happen%20here%20very%20quickly%2C%20in%20the%20next%20day%2C%20two%20days%2C%20three%20days%2C%20next%20week%20or%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20a%20potential%20peace%20deal%20with%20Iran.%20%26quot%3BBeyond%20that%2C%20I%20think%20we've%20got%20a%20real%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZandi%20pointed%20to%20America's%20dwindling%20stockpiles%20of%20oil%2C%20with%20the%20nation's%20Strategic%20Petroleum%20Reserve%20recently%20falling%20to%20365%20million%20barrels%2C%20the%20lowest%20stocks%20have%20been%20in%20about%20two%20years%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eia.gov%2Fpetroleum%2Fsupply%2Fweekly%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEnergy%20Information%20Administration%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbsent%20a%20deal%20with%20Iran%2C%20gas%20prices%20could%20soon%20rise%20to%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgas-prices-us-iran-war-oil-fuel-markets-jpmorgan-goldman-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%245%20a%20barrel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20key%20psychological%20threshold%20for%20consumers%20that%20could%20trigger%20a%20spending%20pullback%20and%20an%20economic%20downturn%2C%20Zandi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrude%20prices%20rising%20over%20%24125%20a%20barrel%20would%20also%20be%20another%20critical%20marker%20that%20could%20suggest%20a%20recession%20is%20coming%20for%20the%20US%20economy%2C%20he%20suggested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20national%20average%20price%20for%20a%20gallon%20of%20regular%20gas%20clocked%20in%20%244.32%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20would%20get%20to%20that%20%245%20a%20gallon%2C%26quot%3B%20Zandi%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20would%20be%2C%20I%20think%2C%20enough%20to%20push%20the%20already%20tenuous%20economy%20into%20a%20recession.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHFI%20Research%2C%20an%20energy%20research%20firm%20that%20recently%20called%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-supply-shock-outlook-breaking-point-global-crude-supply-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epoint%20of%20no%20return%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20oil%20markets%2C%20also%20suggested%20that%20Trump%20had%20a%20matter%20of%20days%20to%20avoid%20severe%20economic%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithin%20hours%2C%20within%20days%2C%20Trump's%20options%20and%20time%20are%20running%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20firm%20wrote%20in%20a%20Substack%20post%20on%20Sunday.%20%26quot%3BBy%20the%20end%20of%20June%2C%20if%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20is%20still%20closed%2C%20global%20oil%20inventory%20operational%20minimum%20is%20guaranteed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Treasury-implied%20probability%20that%20the%20US%20tips%20into%20a%20recession%20within%20the%20next%2012%20months%20clocked%20at%20about%2017%25%20as%20of%20the%20end%20of%20April%2C%20according%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newyorkfed.org%2Fmedialibrary%2Fmedia%2Fresearch%2Fcapital_markets%2Fprob_rec.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanalysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20New%20York%20Fed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-economy-recession-warning-mark-zandi-iran-peace-deal-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780323931000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1d77132e5a80cfe0501be8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-economy-recession-warning-mark-zandi-iran-peace-deal-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Oil%20prices%20could%20soar%20again%20absent%20a%20peace%20deal%20with%20Iran%2C%20Zandi%20said.%20Crude%20saw%20a%20fresh%20spike%20on%20Monday%20as%20US-Iran%20talks%20appeared%20to%20stall.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jsor%40businessinsider.com%20(Jennifer%20Sor)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'I%20want%20my%20marriage'%3A%20Wife%20says%20she's%20deeply%20hurt%20after%20husband%20Graham%20Platner's%20sexting%20with%20other%20women%20becomes%20public%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780323420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131444704%2Cimgsize-157464.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fi-want-my-marriage-wife-says-shes-deeply-hurt-after-husband-graham-platners-sexting-with-other-women-becomes-public%2Farticleshow%2F131444623.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D