%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fi-truly-supported-it-jill-biden-admits-she-wanted-joe-biden-to-pardon-hunter-feared-trump-would-target-their-family%2Famp_articleshow%2F131441605.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fi-truly-supported-it-jill-biden-admits-she-wanted-joe-biden-to-pardon-hunter-feared-trump-would-target-their-family%2Famp_articleshow%2F131441605.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Intel%20and%20AMD%20are%20tumbling%20after%20Nvidia%20muscles%20into%20PC%20chip%20territory%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nvidia%20CO%20Jensen%20Huang%20revealing%20a%20new%20chip%20at%20the%20Computex%202026%20in%20Taipei%20on%20June%201%2C%202026%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1d76432ab5f9757add76ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221760%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EI-HWA%20CHENG%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENvidia%20is%20officially%20getting%20into%20the%20PC%20chip%20game.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20news%20boosted%20Nvidia%20stock%20while%20pushing%20down%20PC%20hardware%20giants%20Intel%20and%20AMD.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENvidia%20says%20the%20new%20chip%20is%20%26quot%3Bdesigned%20for%20AI%2C%20creating%20and%20gaming.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20kicked%20off%20the%20month%20with%20a%20major%20announcement%20of%20a%20new%20frontier%20for%20its%20business%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia's%20reveal%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-computex-keynote-takeaways-ai-laptop-chip-rtx-spark-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20RTX%20Spark%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20Computex%20conference%20in%20Taipei%20sent%20shares%20of%20incumbent%20PC%20hardware%20makers%20tumbling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Famd-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAMD%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fintc-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIntel%3C%2Fa%3E%20dropped%203%25%20and%204%25%2C%20respectively%2C%20while%20Qualcomm%2C%20another%20maker%20of%20PC%20chips%2C%20fell%206%25.%20Nvidia%20jumped%204%25.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRunning%20agents%20securely%20and%20privately%20requires%20hardware%20that's%20up%20to%20the%20task%2C%26quot%3B%20Nvidia%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BDesigned%20for%20AI%2C%20creating%20and%20gaming%2C%20RTX%20Spark%20brings%20NVIDIA's%2030%20years%20of%20technology%20innovation%20to%20slim%20Windows%20laptops%20with%20all-day%20battery%20life%20and%20ultraefficient%20desktop%20PCs.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EDespite%20the%20volatility%20on%20Monday%2C%20AMD%20and%20Intel%20are%20each%20up%20sharply%20year%20to%20date.%20AMD%20is%20up%20130%25%20this%20year%2C%20while%20Intel%20has%20gained%20nearly%20200%25.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20marks%20a%20sharp%20pivot%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fnvda-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Before%20the%20RTX%20Spark%2C%20it's%20presence%20in%20the%20PC%20market%20was%20limited%20to%20graphics%20cards.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20it%20relied%20on%20companies%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fintc-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAMD%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Intel%20to%20provide%20the%20central%20processing%20units%20(CPUs)%20that%20powered%20its%20GeForce%20RTX%20line%2C%20essentially%20functioning%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bbrain%26quot%3B%20of%20each%20machine.%20The%20partnerships%20significantly%20benefitted%20the%20smaller%2C%20rival%20chip%20makers%20who%20struggled%20to%20compete%20in%20an%20industry%20dominated%20by%20Nvidia.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20Nvidia%20is%20setting%20itself%20up%20to%20conquer%20the%20PC%20market%20on%20its%20own%2C%20shifting%20from%20being%20a%20provider%20of%20GPUs%20for%20computing%2C%20to%20a%20direct%20competitor%20for%20the%20companies%20it%20previously%20partnered%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20knee-jerk%20reaction%20is%20this%20Nvidia%20move%20will%20strike%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20PC%20business%20at%20Intel%20and%20AMD%2C%20said%20Chris%20Versace%20of%20TheStreet%20Pro.%20%26quot%3BLogical%20to%20say%20the%20least%2C%20but%20it%20will%20also%20make%20the%20move%20into%20the%20PC%20market%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fqcom-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EQualcomm%3C%2Fa%3E%20(QCOM)%20far%20more%20challenging%20as%20it%20continues%20to%20deal%20with%20issues%20in%20its%20largest%20end%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famd-intel-stock-nvidia-rtx-spark-pc-chip-ai-intc-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780321932000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1d81a32e5a80cfe0501c0a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famd-intel-stock-nvidia-rtx-spark-pc-chip-ai-intc-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nvidia%20is%20jumping%20into%20the%20PC%20chip%20space%2C%20sending%20AMD%20and%20Intel%20stock%20tumbling.%20The%20RTX%20Spark%20was%20revealed%20at%20the%20Computex%20event%20in%20Taipei.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sobrient%40insider.com%20(Samuel%20O'Brient)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A100%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Will%20Dhanush%20enter%20politics%20one%20day%3F%20actor's%20father%20reacts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780321774000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131444236%2Cimgsize-113090.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%2