0in%20Taipei%2C%20Taiwan%2C%20is%20Asia's%20largest%20tech%20trade%20show%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20Huang%20is%20one%20of%20its%20main%20draws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcomputex-taiwan-nvidia-jensen-huang-ai-tech-taipei-semiconductor-chips-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BJensanity%26quot%3B%20around%20Huang%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20grown%20since%20last%20year's%20Computex%2C%20when%20crowds%20flocked%20to%20see%20him%20in%20Taipei.%20At%20this%20year's%20event%2C%20his%20onstage%20dance%20moves%20with%20colleagues%20went%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20key%20takeaways%20from%20his%20keynote%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2202a9bd69-4453-4884-88e1-6e918baeac77%5C%22%3E1.%20Nvidia's%20new%20chip%20brings%20AI%20to%20laptops%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20became%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-share-price-record-first-5-trillion-dollar-company-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emost%20valuable%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20world%20by%20selling%20chips%20for%20data%20centers%20to%20power%20the%20AI%20boom.%20Now%20it%20wants%20to%20power%20AI%20directly%20on%20personal%20computers%2C%20a%20move%20that%20will%20put%20it%20in%20more%20direct%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famd-intel-stock-nvidia-rtx-spark-pc-chip-ai-intc-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecompetition%20with%20Intel%20and%20AMD%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whose%20shares%20tumbled%20on%20Monday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20unveiled%20the%20RTX%20Spark%20%E2%80%94%20a%20chip%20designed%20to%20enable%20AI%20agents%20to%20run%20natively%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsc%2Fheres-why-organizations-should-invest-in-an-ai-personal-computer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epersonal%20computers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Nvidia%20has%20collaborated%20with%20Microsoft%20for%20Windows%20PCs%20purpose-built%20for%20running%20personal%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20gave%20the%20example%20of%20designing%20a%20house%20to%20demonstrate%20what%20an%20AI%20chip%20for%20a%20personal%20computer%20could%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20could%20select%20the%20build%20site%2C%20share%20concept%20sketches%2C%20and%20a%20style%20moodboard%2C%20then%20prompt%20a%20chatbot%20with%20requirements.%20Then%20the%20agent%20gets%20to%20work%2C%20turning%20your%20idea%20into%20a%20plan%2C%20complete%20with%20renderings%20and%20materials%20%E2%80%94%20all%20while%20running%20on%20the%20device%20itself%20rather%20than%20in%20the%20cloud.%20Running%20AI%20locally%20comes%20with%20privacy%20and%20speed%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20reinvention%20of%20the%20computer%20is%20as%20big%20of%20a%20deal%20as%20the%20reinvention%20of%20the%20phone%20into%20what%20we%20now%20know%20as%20the%20smartphone%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e85e2a59-26a5-4aea-ba47-d3aa2d89ebb7%5C%22%3E2.%20Nvidia%20is%20doubling%20down%20as%20an%20'infrastructure%20company'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20said%20it's%20not%20enough%20for%20Nvidia%20to%20just%20design%20AI%20chips%2C%20known%20as%20graphics%20processing%20units%2C%20or%20GPUs.%20He%20wants%20to%20build%20the%20entire%20stack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNvidia%20has%20really%20become%20an%20infrastructure%20company.%20Not%20just%20a%20GPU%20company.%20Not%20just%20a%20systems%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Computex%2C%20he%20unveiled%20the%20Nvidia%20DSX%2C%20a%20framework%20for%20designing%2C%20deploying%2C%20and%20operating%20AI%20factories%20at%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20AI%20factory%20is%20the%20combination%20of%20data%20centers%2C%20power%2C%20cooling%2C%20networking%2C%20compute%2C%20software%2C%20and%20data%20that%20enables%20AI%20to%20be%20trained%20and%20operated%20at%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecoming%20incredibly%20good%20at%20helping%20customers%20build%20AI%20factories%20and%20deploy%20AI%20factories%20is%20incredibly%20important%2C%20and%20the%20reason%20for%20that%20is%20this%3A%20compute%20is%20revenue%20now.%20Compute%20is%20profit%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20also%20announced%20on%20Sunday%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethat%20the%20Vera%20Rubin%2C%20a%20microprocessor%20designed%20to%20power%20AI%20agents%2C%20is%20now%20in%20full%20production.%20The%20company%20previously%20announced%20that%20Anthropic%2C%20SpaceX%2C%20and%20OpenAI%20are%20among%20its%20first%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f3f51dc2-5144-4f64-b5c0-f4ea2a7ab976%5C%22%3E3.%20Huang%20says%20AI%20will%20need%20more%20software%20engineers%2C%20not%20less%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20reiterated%20his%20optimistic%20view%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-nvidia-anthropic-dario-amodei-ai-jobs-vivatech-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI's%20impact%20on%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20believes%20that%20the%20productivity%20gains%20AI%20provides%20to%20software%20engineers%20will%20instead%20make%20the%20profession%20more%20valuable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20talk%20about%20AI%20reducing%20jobs%20%E2%80%94%20complete%20nonsense%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20causing%20more%20software%20engineers%20to%20be%20hired%2C%20and%20the%20reason%20for%20that%20is%20very%20simple.%20If%20you%20can%20hire%20a%20software%20engineer%20and%20you%20can%20generate%20%249%20trillion%20worth%20of%20productive%20work%2C%20why%20wouldn't%20you%20want%20to%20hire%20more%20software%20engineers%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20has%20transformed%20the%20role%20of%20software%20engineers.%20For%20some%20of%20them%2C%20it%20has%20created%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-creating-identity-crisis-for-software-engineers-coders-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eidentity%20crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20others%20worry%20that%20they'll%20be%20automated%20out%20of%20a%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20data%20from%20tech-hiring%20analytics%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-isnt-killing-software-coding-jobs-booming-trueup-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efirm%20TrueUp%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%20that%20software%20engineering%20job%20openings%20have%20actually%20increased%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Huang%20said%20onstage%20at%20Computex%20that%20AI%20means%20it's%20actually%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-incredible-time-software-company-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bincredible%20time%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20a%20software%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20following%20concerns%20that%20the%20technology%20would%20cause%20a%20%26quot%3BSaaSpocalypse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-computex-keynote-takeaways-ai-laptop-chip-rtx-spark-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780317284000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1d61242e5a80cfe0501b90%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-computex-keynote-takeaways-ai-laptop-chip-rtx-spark-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jensen%20Huang's%20speech%20was%20jam-packed%20with%20new%20releases%2C%20including%20the%20RTX%20Spark%20which%20aims%20to%20reinvent%20the%20personal%20computer%20as%20we%20know%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rshahidi%40insider.com%20(Roya%20Shahidi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22K%20Annamalai%20Likely%20To%20Quit%20BJP%2C%20Launch%20Own%20Party%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22K%20Annamalai%2C%20IPS%20officer-turned-politician%2C%20was%20offered%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV.%20The%2041-year-old%20le