%20happy%20accident%20that%20helped%20change%20the%20way%20we%20eat.%20He%20believed%20pizza%20was%20the%20perfect%20vehicle%20for%20California's%20bounty%20of%20fresh%20ingredients%20and%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20his%20pizza%20chef%20Ed%20LaDou%2C%20elevated%20the%20humble%20pie%20to%20a%20gourmet%20specialty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20locals%20and%20celebrities%20couldn't%20get%20enough.%20Johnny%20Carson%20was%20known%20to%20order%2010%20pizzas%20at%20a%20time%20and%20stick%20them%20in%20his%20freezer%2C%20inspiring%20Puck%20to%20launch%20a%20frozen-food%20empire%2C%20and%20the%20smoked%20salmon%20pizza%20has%20been%20served%20at%20the%20official%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-wolfgang-puck-dishes-out-30-000-plates-oscars-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOscars%20after-party%3C%2Fa%3E%20every%20year%20since%201994.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20book%20a%20trip%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-cheese-store-of-beverly-hills-dominick-dibartolomeo-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBeverly%20Hills%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20get%20nominated%20for%20an%20Academy%20Award%20to%20enjoy%20the%20pizza.%20I%20went%20behind%20the%20scenes%20at%20Spago%2C%20where%20the%20pie%20was%20invented%2C%20to%20learn%20how%20Puck%20makes%20his%20most%20iconic%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWolfgang%20Puck's%20smoked%20salmon%20pizza%20was%20inspired%20by%20a%20request%20from%20Joan%20Collins.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smoked%20salmon%20pizza%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f4fbbc9a23d20d291b58c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStella%20Kalinina%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20actress%20came%20into%20Spago%20one%20day%20in%201982%2C%20the%20year%20Puck%20opened%20the%20restaurant%2C%20and%20requested%20smoked%20salmon%20with%20brioche.%20Puck%20had%20run%20out%20of%20bread%20but%20knew%20he%20needed%20to%20do%20something%20to%20keep%20the%20famously%20fiery%20%26quot%3BDynasty%26quot%3B%20star%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20want%20to%20make%20Joan%20Collins%20mad%2C%26quot%3B%20Puck%20joked%20in%20his%202021%20documentary%20%26quot%3BWolfgang.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPuck%20got%20the%20idea%20to%20add%20smoked%20salmon%20to%20baked%20pizza%20dough.%20He%20paired%20the%20salmon%20with%20cr%C3%A8me%20fra%C3%AEche%20and%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcaviar-trend-fast-food-desserts-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edollops%20of%20caviar%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20impress%20Collins%2C%20who%2C%20at%20the%20time%2C%20was%20the%20highest-paid%20actress%20on%20TV.%20The%20unusual%20dish%20was%20an%20instant%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20had%20no%20tomato%20sauce%3B%20it%20had%20no%20cheese%2C%26quot%3B%20legendary%20chef%20Nancy%20Silverton%2C%20who%20got%20her%20start%20at%20Spago%2C%20recalled%20in%20the%20documentary.%20%26quot%3BAs%20simple%20as%20that%20sounds%20today%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20anyone%20had%20done%20a%20pizza%20like%20that%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20smoked%20salmon%20pizza%20had%20a%20huge%20influence%20on%20Puck's%20son%2C%20now%20president%20of%20the%20Wolfgang%20Puck%20Fine%20Dining%20Group.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Making%20smoked%20salmon%20pizza%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f4fc049a23d20d291b58ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStella%20Kalinina%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Byron%20Lazaroff-Puck%20was%20in%20kindergarten%2C%20his%20parents%20organized%20a%20field%20trip%20to%20Spago%20for%20his%20class.%20The%205-year-olds%20were%20given%20mini%20chef%20coats%20and%20hats%20to%20wear%20while%20Puck%20showed%20them%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feasy-homemade-pizza-dough-recipe-bread-machine-steps-photos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehow%20to%20make%20pizza%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20always%20look%20back%20on%20that%20really%20fondly%2C%20because%20it%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20felt%20really%20proud%20about%20what%20my%20family%20did%2C%26quot%3B%20Lazaroff-Puck%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20as%20I%20grew%20up%20and%20started%20working%20in%20the%20restaurants%2C%20it%20was%20always%20the%20station%20I%20felt%20so%20enamored%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20smoked%20salmon%20pizza%20was%20also%20one%20of%20the%20first%20dishes%20to%20spark%20Lazaroff-Puck's%20interest%20in%20cooking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20this%20confluence%20of%20flavors%20that%20is%20built%20upon%20multiple%20layers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20seminal%20in%20my%20own%20creative%20journey%20of%20getting%20interested%20in%20food.%20To%20be%20able%20to%20now%20teach%20it%20to%20others%2C%20too%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20coolest%20things%20I%20could%20ask%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20with%20that%2C%20it%20was%20my%20turn%20to%20learn!%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20began%20by%20gathering%20the%20ingredients%20and%20molding%20the%20pizza%20dough.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Making%20smoked%20salmon%20pizza%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f4fbbcab24bc0b23a1888c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStella%20Kalinina%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20make%20Puck's%20smoked%20salmon%20pizza%20at%20home%2C%20you'll%20need%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E6%20ounces%20of%20pizza%20dough%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E1%20tablespoon%20of%20chili%20and%20garlic%20oil%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%C2%BC%20cup%20of%20thinly%20sliced%20red%20onion%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2%20tablespoons%20of%20dill%20cream%20(dill-infused%20cr%C3%A8me%20fra%C3%AEche)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2.5%20ounces%20of%20thinly%20sliced%20smoked%20salmon%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E1%20teaspoon%20of%20chopped%20fresh%20chives%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E1%20tablespoon%20of%20sevruga%20caviar%20(optional)%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20flouring%20the%20counter%20to%20prevent%20the%20dough%20from%20sticking%2C%20Lazaroff-Puck%20showed%20me%20how%20to%20stretch%20the%20dough%20into%20an%208-inch%20circle.%20The%20outer%20edge%2C%20he%20noted%2C%20should%20be%20a%20little%20thicker%20than%20the%20inner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThen%20we%20brushed%20the%20dough%20with%20oil%E2%80%A6%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Making%20smoked%20salmon%20pizza%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f4fbbc9a23d20d291b58c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStella%20Kalinina%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20don't%20have%20chili%20and%20garlic%20oil%20on%20hand%2C%20you%20can%20always%20use%20olive%20oil!%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%E2%80%A6%20and%20added%20the%20red%20onion.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Making%20smoked%20salmon%20pizza%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f4fbbcab24bc0b23a1888d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStella%20Kalinina%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20sprinkled%20the%20red%20onion%20slices%20evenly%20over%20the%20dough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20dough%20is%20baked%20in%20Spago's%20wood-fired%20pizza%20oven.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Making%20smoked%20salmon%20pizza%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f4fc04ab24bc0b23a18894%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStella%20Kalinina%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20making%20this%20at%20home%2C%20Lazaroff-Puck%20recommends%20preheating%20the%20oven%20to%20500%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20and%20baking%20the%20dough%20on%20a%20pizza%20stone%20placed%20on%20the%20middle%20rack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20know%20the%20crust%20is%20ready%20when%20it's%20golden%20brown%2C%20which%20should%20take%20around%20six%20to%20eight%20minutes.%20Remove%20the%20pizza%20from%20the%20oven%20and%20set%20it%20on%20a%20firm%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20pizza%20crust%20is%20topped%20with%20Spago's%20dill%20cream.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Making%20smoked%20salmon%20pizza%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f4fbbcab24bc0b23a1888a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStella%20Kalinina%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20make%20the%20cream%20ahead%20of%20time%20by%20mixing%20some%20cr%C3%A8me%20fra%C3%AEche%20with%20chopped%20dill.%20Add%20extra%20flavor%20with%20chopped%20shallots%2C%20a%20squeeze%20of%20lemon%2C%20and%20some%20salt%20and%20pepper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThen%20it's%20time%20to%20layer%20the%20smoked%20salmon%20slices.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Making%20smoked%20salmon%20pizza%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f4fbbc9a23d20d291b58c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStella%20Kalinina%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESpago's%20executive%20chef%20Ari%20Rosenson%2C%20who%20began%20working%20at%20the%20restaurant%20when%20he%20was%2016%2C%20said%20the%20salmon%20is%20butchered%20and%20smoked%20in-house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20recipe%20has%20been%20altered%20very%20little%20over%20the%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20got%20all%20the%20little%20things%20you%20look%20for%20in%20a%20good%20dish%20%E2%80%94%20sweet%2C%20sour%2C%20it%20just%20hits%20all%20the%20marks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20followed%20Lazaroff-Puck's%20advice%20and%20arranged%20the%20slices%20of%20salmon%20so%20that%20they%20covered%20the%20entire%20pizza%2C%20making%20sure%20they%20slightly%20overlapped%20along%20the%20inner%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20pizza%20is%20topped%20with%20chopped%20chives%20and%20dollops%20of%20caviar.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Making%20smoked%20salmon%20pizza%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f4fbbcab24bc0b23a1888b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStella%20Kalinina%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20using%20caviar%20at%20home%2C%20Lazaroff-Puck%20recommends%20adding%20a%20small%20spoonful%20to%20the%20center%20of%20each%20slice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOne%20bite%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20see%20why%20Puck's%20smoked%20salmon%20pizza%20has%20been%20a%20classic%20for%20over%2040%20years.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Eating%20smoked%20salmon%20pizza%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f4fbbc3022d9b19bbffaab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStella%20Kalinina%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20chef%20Rosenson%20said%2C%20Puck's%20pizza%20hits%20every%20mark.%20The%20crust%20has%20that%20satisfying%20crackle%20from%20the%20wood-fired%20oven%2C%20the%20cr%C3%A8me%20fra%C3%AEche%20is%20light%20and%20bright%2C%20and%20the%20smoked%20salmon%20paired%20with%20caviar%20tastes%20like%20luxury%20personified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20fun%2C%20it's%20unexpected%2C%20and%2C%20frankly%2C%20it's%20iconic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20the%20above%20could%20also%20be%20said%20of%20Puck%2C%20who%2C%2