ted%20prosperity%2C%20and%20he%20believes%20AI%20will%20too.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20layoffs%20mount%2C%20economists%20and%20CEOs%20are%20increasingly%20challenging%20AI%20job-loss%20narratives.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20debate%20rages%20on%20about%20whether%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-ai-jobs-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20is%20eliminating%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Bill%20Gurley%20thinks%20many%20of%20today's%20fears%20echo%20a%20historical%20mistake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20longtime%20venture%20capitalist%20said%20on%20a%20recent%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BAll-In%20Podcast%26quot%3B%20that%20warnings%20about%20AI%20destroying%20jobs%20look%20like%20concerns%20raised%20during%20the%20Industrial%20Revolution%20%E2%80%94%20concerns%20he%20said%20ultimately%20proved%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGurley%20pointed%20to%20Pope%20Leo%20XIII's%201891%20encyclical%2C%20%26quot%3BRerum%20Novarum%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20warned%20that%20the%20Industrial%20Revolution%20and%20the%20rise%20of%20industrial%20capitalism%20could%20harm%20workers%20and%20widen%20social%20inequality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20comparison%20came%20as%20the%20hosts%20discussed%20a%20recent%20AI-focused%20encyclical%20from%20Pope%20Leo%20XIV%2C%20the%20current%20pope%2C%20who%20warned%20that%20mass%20AI-driven%20unemployment%20could%20become%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpope-leo-ai-encyclical-magnifica-humanitas-takeaways-jobs-developers-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrue%20social%20calamity%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLeo%20the%2013th%20encyclical%20warned%20that%20the%20industrial%20revolution%20was%20going%20to%20be%20bad%20for%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Gurley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20century%20that%20followed%20delivered%20a%20dramatic%20rise%20in%20living%20standards%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20workweek%20went%20from%20over%2060%20hours%20to%2034%20hours%20globally.%20Real%20wages%20went%20up%208%20to%2010x%20adjusted%20for%20inflation%2C%26quot%3B%20Gurley%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20life%20expectancy%20rose%2C%20workplace%20deaths%20declined%2C%20and%20global%20poverty%20fell%20from%20roughly%2075%25%20of%20humanity%20to%20under%2010%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20of%20the%20broader%20trends%20Gurley%20cited%20are%20well%20documented%2C%20some%20of%20the%20specific%20figures%20are%20difficult%20to%20verify.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20from%20the%20UN's%20International%20Labour%20Organization%20%E2%80%94%20its%20agency%20for%20the%20world%20of%20work%20%E2%80%94%20showed%20that%20the%20average%20worker%20globally%20worked%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ilo.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fwcmsp5%2Fgroups%2Fpublic%2F%2540ed_protect%2F%2540protrav%2F%2540travail%2Fdocuments%2Fpublication%2Fwcms_864222.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E43.9%20hours%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20week%20before%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20economists%20broadly%20agree%20that%20real%20wages%20have%20risen%20dramatically%20since%20the%20Industrial%20Revolution%2C%20the%20gains%20have%20been%20far%20less%20pronounced%20for%20typical%20US%20workers%20in%20recent%20decades.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epi.org%2Ffeature%2Fplaceholder-13-wages%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EResearch%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Economic%20Policy%20Institute%20shows%20that%20since%201979%2C%20productivity%20has%20grown%20roughly%20eight%20times%20faster%20than%20pay%20for%20typical%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20those%20things%20happened%20because%20of%20technology%2C%20innovation%2C%20and%20capitalism%2C%20which%20is%20exactly%20what%20Leo%20the%2013th%20was%20warning%20against%2C%26quot%3B%20Gurley%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20he%20got%20it%20dead%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investor%20said%20he%20sees%20no%20reason%20to%20believe%20AI%20will%20break%20that%20historical%20pattern.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHistorically%2C%20innovation%20has%20led%20to%20more%20prosperity%20for%20humans%2C%26quot%3B%20Gurley%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20see%20no%20reason%20why%20that%20won't%20happen%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228587ef63-362c-4867-8a7a-df9dcc9adc88%5C%22%3EThe%20AI%20jobs%20debate%20is%20shifting%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGurley's%20view%20reflects%20a%20growing%20pushback%20against%20AI%20doomerism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApollo%20chief%20economist%20Torsten%20Sl%C3%B8k%20said%20in%20May%20that%20there%20is%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-jobs-crisis-no-evidence-apollo-chief-economist-torsten-slok-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ezero%20evidence%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20that%20AI%20is%20causing%20job%20losses%2C%20while%20Goldman%20Sachs%20CEO%20David%20Solomon%20said%20that%20the%20technology%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20automate%20tasks%20than%20eliminate%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20AI's%20most%20prominent%20voices%2C%20including%20OpenAI%20CEO%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-ai-jobs-prediction-wrong-white-collar-openai-australia-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20softened%20earlier%20predictions%20of%20widespread%20unemployment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20many%20major%20companies%20including%20Block%2C%20Cloudflare%2C%20Cisco%2C%20IBM%2C%20Coinbase%2C%20and%20Snap%20have%20cited%20AI%20as%20a%20factor%20in%20recent%20layoffs%20%E2%80%94%20a%20trend%20some%20economists%20and%20industry%20leaders%20believe%20may%20overstate%20the%20technology's%20impact%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fforget-ai-heres-the-real-reason-the-job-market-sucks-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edownplay%20other%20pressures%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20years%20of%20overhiring%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20higher%20interest%20rates%2C%20inflation%2C%20budget-cutting%20initiatives%2C%20and%20uncertainty%20around%20trade%20policy%20and%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Gurley%20said%20that%20automation%20could%20reshape%20some%20types%20of%20jobs%2C%20he%20said%20that%20workers%20who%20embrace%20AI%20tools%20will%20be%20better%20positioned%20than%20those%20who%20resist%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20best%20way%20to%20protect%20yourself%20from%20AI%20is%20to%20be%20the%20most%20AI-enabled%20version%20of%20yourself%20you%20can%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-gurley-says-ai-job-fears-echo-a-historic-mistake-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780312323000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1d59062ab5f9757add7648%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-gurley-says-ai-job-fears-echo-a-historic-mistake-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20veteran%20VC%20says%20innovation%20has%20historically%20created%20prosperity%2C%20and%20he%20believes%20AI%20will%20too.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tspirlet%40insider.com%20(Thibault%20Spirlet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%2C%2026%2C%20Rapes%2080-Year-Old%20Woman%20in%20UP's%20Hathras%2C%20Arrested%3A%20Cops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22An%20elderly%20woman%20was%20allegedly%20raped%20by%20her%2028-year-old%20neighbour%20at%20her%20residence%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Hathras%20on%20Monday%2C%20police%20said.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780312314000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F0htt5beg_india-police-generic_625x300_23_December_22.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-26-rapes-80-year-old-woman-in-ups-hathras-arreste