on%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jill%20Gardner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJill%20Gardner%20leads%20a%20team%20of%20more%20than%20500%20family%20members%20who%20own%20Laird%20Norton.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20married%20into%20the%20company%2C%20and%20it%20has%20changed%20how%20she%20thinks%20about%20family%20connections.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20family%20holds%20annual%20summits%20and%20hosts%20camps%20for%20the%20youngest%20generations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3EJill%20Gardner%3Cem%3E%2C%20family%20president%20at%20the%20Laird%20Norton%20Company.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20married%20my%20husband%2C%20Doug%2C%20I%20also%20married%20into%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-nyc-joined-family-business-career-decision-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamily%20business%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20his%20cousins%20are%20the%20fifth%20generation%20of%20his%20family%20to%20own%20the%20Laird%20Norton%20Company.%20The%20business%20was%20founded%20in%201855%20by%20two%20brothers%20and%20their%20cousin%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flumber-wood-prices-americas-economic-future-real-estate-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elumber%20operation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Today%2C%20we're%20an%20investment%20firm%20that's%20involved%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%2024%20when%20I%20got%20married%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20clue%20what%20was%20going%20on%20with%20the%20business.%20That%20started%20to%20change%20when%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-have-big-age-gap-motherhood-is-different-this-time-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edaughter%20was%20born%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20really%20started%20to%20pay%20attention%20to%20how%20unusual%20this%20legacy%20is.%20As%20I%20read%20up%20on%20our%20family%20history%2C%20I%20became%20absolutely%20fascinated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225295daac-e8c2-4525-a595-f57da3ee57b3%5C%22%3EThe%20business%20keeps%20distant%20cousins%20connected%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20nuclear%20family%20with%20two%20brothers.%20We%20love%20each%20other%2C%20but%20we%20don't%20have%20a%20lot%20in%20common.%20There's%20no%20shared%20goal%20keeping%20us%20close%2C%20especially%20now%20that%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdads-dementia-care-cost-life-savings-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparents%20have%20died%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20sometimes%20keeping%20in%20touch%20feels%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20husband's%20family%20%E2%80%94%20now%20my%20family%20%E2%80%94%20the%20company%20fills%20that%20role.%20Today%2C%20there%20are%20551%20family%20members%20in%20seven%20countries%20who%20all%20share%20the%20common%20experience%20of%20owning%20and%20helping%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworked-at-my-mothers-business-alongside-sister-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erun%20the%20family%20business%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20plays%20an%20active%20role%20in%20running%20the%20company%20and%20forming%20its%20strategic%20planning.%20Family%20members%20elect%20the%20board%20of%20directors%2C%20which%20has%20seven%20family%20members%20and%20five%20non-family%20members%2C%20including%20the%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20this%2C%20our%20extended%20family%20has%20more%20in%20common%20than%20just%20being%20distant%20cousins.%20We%20disagree%20about%20everything%20under%20the%20sun%2C%20but%20agree%20about%20making%20the%20right%20decision%20for%20the%20company.%20We%20share%20an%20affinity%20for%20the%20business%20because%20it's%20part%20of%20our%20family%20legacy.%20I%20came%20to%20really%20respect%20and%20admire%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222443db3c-43cc-45ec-8bd5-515eda003401%5C%22%3EWe%20produce%20a%20journal%20and%20host%20events%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELucky%20for%20me%2C%20the%20Laird%20Norton%20family%20has%20always%20been%20very%20open%20to%20bringing%20married-in%20family%20members%20into%20the%20business.%20Part%20of%20that%20was%20through%20necessity.%20Most%20of%20the%20second%20generation%20of%20the%20family%20were%20women%2C%20so%20the%20men%20they%20married%20were%20brought%20to%20the%20table.%20Today%2C%20not%20all%20spouses%20take%20ownership%20of%20the%20company%2C%20but%20they%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20family%20president%20of%20the%20company%2C%20my%20role%20is%20to%20keep%20family%20members%20engaged.%20I%20help%20produce%20the%20Laird%20Norton%20family%20journal%2C%20which%20is%20somewhat%20similar%20to%20an%20alumni%20magazine.%20It's%20a%20place%20for%20the%20family%20to%20tell%20its%20story%20%E2%80%94%20everything%20from%20writing%20about%20personal%20interests%2C%20to%20sharing%20family%20trips%2C%20to%20announcing%20new%20babies%20and%20spouses.%20We've%20recently%20welcomed%20the%20first%208th-generation%20member%20of%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20get%20together%20each%20year.%20This%20summer%2C%20about%20350%20family%20members%20will%20meet%20in%20Salt%20Lake%20City%20for%20our%20annual%20summit.%20That's%20where%20we%20have%20a%20stakeholder%20meeting%20and%20talk%20about%20goals.%20Of%20course%2C%20it's%20fun%20too.%20My%20children%2C%20who%20are%20now%20grown%2C%20loved%20going%20to%20these%20events%20to%20catch%20up%20with%20their%20cousins.%20That%20created%20an%20authentic%2C%20genuine%20connection%20as%20they%20carry%20this%20legacy%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225739bc67-080e-4335-807d-7443404a1949%5C%22%3EWe%20focus%20on%20keeping%20younger%20family%20members%20engaged%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20saying%20with%20family%20business%20that%20most%20go%20%26quot%3Bshirtsleeves%20to%20shirtsleeves%26quot%3B%20in%20three%20generations%2C%20meaning%20the%20wealth%20is%20built%2C%20then%20lost%20again.%20That%20might%20have%20happened%20with%20Laird%20Norton%2C%20but%20we%20had%20a%20third-generation%20family%20member%20with%20the%20drive%20of%20a%20founder.%20He%20helped%20establish%20a%20company%20that%20could%20stand%20the%20test%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20husband%20was%20growing%20up%2C%20the%20company%20was%20less%20intentional%20about%20engaging%20family%20members.%20The%20cousins%20who%20are%20his%20age%20jokingly%20call%20themselves%20%26quot%3Bthe%20lost%20generation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20they've%20completely%20changed%20things%20for%20their%20children%20and%20grandchildren%20by%20being%20very%20intentional%20about%20bringing%20younger%20generations%20into%20the%20fold.%20During%20our%20summit%2C%20we%20run%20a%20camp%20for%20kids.%20Beginning%20at%2014%2C%20family%20members%20can%20attend%20the%20business%20overview%20meetings.%20We%20have%20an%20internship%20program%20to%20help%20family%20members%20learn%20about%20the%20company%2C%20and%20a%20bi-annual%20%26quot%3Bnext%20gen%26quot%3B%20event%20specifically%20to%20engage%20family%20members%20age%2021-40.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EContinuing%20to%20hold%20an%20eighth-generation%20business%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20work.%20Having%20events%20that%20foster%20connection%20with%20the%20company%20and%20the%20cousins%20helps%20us%20ensure%20the%20Laird%20Norton%20family%20legacy%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-leading-multigenerational-family-busines-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780310041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a023d48ba7ef34b41f37288%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-leading-multigenerational-family-busines-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jill%20Gardner%20helps%20lead%20her%20husband's%2