t%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-property-taxes-texas-moving-new-mexico-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHouston's%20property%20tax%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20among%20the%20highest%20in%20the%20country%20because%20we%20have%20no%20state%20income%20tax.%20A%20lot%20of%20people%20hate%20on%20Houston%2C%20but%20the%20city%20has%20so%20much%20to%20offer.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20afford%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20in%20Houston%2C%20I%20work%20to%20increase%20my%20income%20and%20live%20below%20my%20means.%20Regardless%20of%20how%20much%20money%20I%20bring%20in%2C%20I%20practice%20responsible%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226009c5f7-d100-4198-82e8-f3dc6df087cf%5C%22%3EI%20have%20multiple%20streams%20of%20income%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20worked%20in%20the%20energy%20industry%20for%2015%20years%20and%20currently%20work%20at%20a%20company%20with%20lucrative%20compensation%20benefits%20(e.g.%2C%20a%20defined%20contribution%20plan%20and%20RSUs).%20I'm%20on%20a%20hybrid%20schedule%2C%20working%20in%20the%20office%20two%20to%20three%20days%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20commute%20is%20about%2025%20minutes%20each%20way.%20My%20healthcare%20comes%20with%20my%20job%20for%20%2492%20a%20month%2C%20and%20it's%20pretty%20easy%20to%20set%20appointments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20investments%2C%20I%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-build-a-portfolio-rental-properties-real-estate-investing-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erental%20property%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20pays%20me%20%242%2C900%20a%20month%20and%20a%20private%20equity%20investment%20that%20pays%20me%20%241%2C250%20a%20month.%20I've%20also%20started%20to%20earn%20some%20side%20income%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmorgan.on.money%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20media%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20social%20media%20because%20there's%20more%20to%20life%20than%20corporate%20work%2C%20and%20there's%20so%20much%20to%20be%20made%20on%20these%20platforms.%20I%20currently%20have%20an%20agent%20pitching%20me%20for%20deals%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20in%20the%20value%20of%20building%20a%20monetizable%20personal%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228b159451-9796-466d-b4b0-29b8efbbb9f3%5C%22%3EI%20plan%20to%20sell%20the%20%24465%2C000%203-bedroom%20townhouse%20I%20purchased%20in%202025%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20live%20in%20the%20Rice%20Military%20neighborhood%2C%20which%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouston-best-city-in-america-2014-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efive%20miles%20from%20downtown%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20extremely%20walkable%2C%20there%20are%20multiple%20green%20spaces%2C%20and%20my%20family%20lives%20nearby.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20house%20payment%20is%20%243%2C186%20a%20month%2C%20plus%20about%20%24300%20in%20utilities%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20HOA.%20It's%20my%20second%20home%2C%20and%20I%20turned%20my%20first%20into%20a%20rental.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuying%20real%20estate%20is%20a%20huge%20commitment%2C%20and%20this%20one%20turned%20into%20a%20nightmare%20with%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20in%20repairs.%20If%20I%20had%20just%20taken%20all%20the%20money%20I%20spent%20on%20this%20house%20and%20invested%20it%20in%20the%20market%2C%20I%20could've%20been%20much%20closer%20to%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretiring-tech-early-coast-fire-make-me-millionaire-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoast%20FIRE%3C%2Fa%3E%20goal%20of%20%241.3%20million.%20I'll%20probably%20sell%20this%20house%2C%20invest%20the%20proceeds%2C%20and%20move%20back%20into%20my%20more%20modest%20rental%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2204e2c6eb-83fd-4c4e-bf97-9a2734367454%5C%22%3EHere's%20how%20I%20budget%20to%20live%20below%20my%20means%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20net%20worth%20is%20%241.1%20million%20in%20savings%20and%20investments.%20To%20get%20around%2C%20I%20drive%20a%202019%20Mazda%20CX5%20that%20I%20bought%20used.%20She%20gets%20me%20from%20point%20A%20to%20point%20B%2C%20and%20I%20plan%20to%20drive%20her%20until%20I%20can%20no%20longer%20do%20so.%20I%20have%20zero%20interest%20in%20upgrading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20budget%20about%20%24400%20per%20month%20for%20groceries%20and%20rarely%20go%20out%20or%20order%20delivery.%20I%20don't%20drink%20coffee%20every%20day%2C%20though%20on%20Saturday%2C%20I%20might%20walk%20to%20treat%20myself%20to%20a%20coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20partner%20and%20I%20are%20currently%20debating%20whether%20we%20want%20to%20spend%20%2450%2C000%20for%20a%20wedding%20or%20save%20that%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20save%20money%2C%20I%20believe%20in%20living%20below%20my%20means%3A%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclothes-to-spend-more-on-what-items-buy-cheap-stylist-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esimple%20wardrobe%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20of%20natural%20fibers%20that%20lasts%20longer%20than%20a%20single%20wear%2C%20buying%20secondhand%20vintage%2C%20accepting%20hand-me-down%20furniture%2C%20and%20eating%20most%20meals%20at%20home.%20I%20also%20go%20without%20expensive%20hair%20and%20eyelash%20extensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221530d968-09fd-4d8d-9f7b-6edf62e0f8e9%5C%22%3EI%20prefer%20the%20city%20over%20the%20suburbs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20never%20lived%20in%20the%20suburbs%2C%20and%20don't%20think%20I'd%20want%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20trade-off%20to%20living%20in%20the%20city%20is%20the%20outdoors%3A%20my%20partner%20loves%20hiking%20and%20other%20outdoor%20activities%2C%20and%20we%20can't%20really%20do%20that%20here.%20Also%2C%20the%20suburbs%20offer%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-family-to-suburbs-texas-benefits-cons-katy-houston-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebetter%20dollar-per-square-foot%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20I%20like%20being%20able%20to%20walk%20everywhere%2C%20so%20I%20think%20that's%20a%20better%20trade-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20possible%20that%20if%20I%20have%20kids%2C%20we%20might%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-moved-from-city-to-suburbs-why-ill-stay%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emove%20to%20the%20suburbs%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20better%20schools.%20I'm%20still%20deciding%20on%20whether%20it's%20worth%20it%20to%20have%20kids%2C%20which%20I%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20millennials%20are%20contemplating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2208cad2c9-1ff8-4a49-911b-9f80a23578cb%5C%22%3ELiving%20in%20Houston%20is%20worth%20it%20to%20me%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Houston%2C%20we%20have%20lots%20of%20high-paying%20jobs%2C%20access%20to%20great%20amenities%2C%20and%20sports%20teams.%20We're%20even%20hosting%20the%20World%20Cup%20this%20summer.%20There's%20a%20huge%20Vietnamese%20community%20with%20delicious%20food%3B%20it%20may%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20diverse%20cities%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20spent%20a%20good%20amount%20on%20dining%20out%20this%20past%20year%20and%20my%20gym%20membership.%20Another%20splurge%20is%20golf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20I%20plan%20to%20invest%20over%20%24100%2C000%20this%20year%20and%20save%20or%20invest%2053%25%20of%20my%20gross%20income.%20It's%20definitely%20worth%20it%20to%20me%20to%20live%20in%20Houston%2C%20and%20I%20have%20no%20plans%20on%20moving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20want%20to%20share%20your%20cost%20of%20living%20with%20Business%20Insider%3F%20Email%20editor%20Tess%20Martinelli%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Atmartinelli%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Etmartinelli%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-houston-resident-budgets-and-saves-over-half-285k-income-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780305121000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1c044a2e5a80cfe0501959%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-houston-resident-budgets-and-saves-over-half-285k-income-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Houston%20resident%20shares%20how%20she%20budgets%20to%20live%20below%20her%20means%20with%20a%20%24285%2C000%20income.%20A%20used%20car%2C%20secondhand%20clothes%2C%20and%20rental%20property%20are%20key.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kaila%20Yu)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Baltimore%20man%20started%20an%20income-sharing%20club%20after%20the%20DOGE%20job%20cuts.%20It's%20redistributed%20over%20%2420%2C000%20so%20far.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223693%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alex%20Zhu%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1cb5892ab5f9757add7512%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222948%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlex%20Zhu%20founded%20the%20Baltimore%20Community%20Guaranteed%20Income%20Club%20in%202025.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Zhu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAlex%20Zhu%20founded%20the%20Baltimore%20Community%20Guaranteed%20Income%20Club%20in%20April%202025.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20he%20created%20the%20club%20after%20his%20friends%20lost%20their%20jobs%20in%20the%20DOGE%20cuts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAbout%2050%20Baltimore%20neighbors%20now%20participate%20in%20the%20income-sharing%20club%2C%20and%20it%20continues%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-department-of-government-efficiency%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDOGE%20quietly%20disbanded%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20late%20November%2C%20Elon%20Musk%20had%20returned%20his%20attention%20to%20his%20companies.%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20was%20focused%20on%20his%20immigration%20crackdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Alex%20Zhu%2C%20though%2C%20the%20impact%20of%20those%20months%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-layoffs-lost-usaid-job-year-ago-feel-survivors-guilt-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efrenzied%20job%20cuts%3C%2Fa%3E%20lingered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZhu's%20friends%20and%20neighbors%20were%20among%20the%20more%20than%20260%2C000%20federal%20employees%20dispatched%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20bunch%20of%20friends%20who%20worked%20in%20public%20and%20global%20health%20in%20the%20federal%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhu%2C%2029%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThey%20all%20got%20laid%20off%20and%20were%20facing%20uncertainty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20uncertainty%20took%20many%20forms%3A%20rising%20grocery%20costs%2C%20pricey%20healthcare%2C%20fluctuating%20childcare%20expenses.%20The%20list%20went%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20Zhu%20decided%20to%20start%20a%20local%20income-sharing%20program%20he%20called%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Falexzhu.substack.com%2Fp%2Fbaltimore-community-based-guaranteed%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBaltimore%20Community%20Guaranteed%20Income%20Club%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20club%20launched%20in%20April%202025%2C%20mostly%20to%20support%20his%20friends%20and%20other%20community%20members%20who%20were%20unemployed%20or%20close%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20participate%20in%20the%20club%2C%20residents%20pledge%207%25%20of%20their%20monthly%20post-tax%20income.%20Zhu%20calculates%20the%20average%20income%20among%20them%20and%2C%20with%20a%20few%20dozen%20lines%20of%20code%2C%20determines%20which%20residents%20are%20above%20the%20monthly%20average%20and%20which%20are%20below.%20Those%20making%20above%20the%20average%20send%20money%20directly%20to%20those%20below%20it%20via%20Venmo%20or%20Zelle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20first%20year%2C%20Zhu%20said%20the%20club%20redistributed%20some%20%2420%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMembers%20find%20out%20how%20much%20to%20give%20and%20who%20to%20give%20it%20to%20through%20Airtable.%20The%20specific%20monetary%20amount%20is%20determined%20by%20the%20number%20of%20members%20and%20their%20monthly%20average%20income.%20There%20is%20no%20pooling%20of%20money%2C%20and%20Zhu%20said%20the%20process%20is%20decentralized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20program%20that%20we%20run%20is%20functionally%20unemployment%20insurance%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhu%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20serves%20two%20purposes%3A%20Helping%20friends%20who%20need%20it%20and%20also%20warming%20people%20up%20to%20the%20idea%20that%20this%20is%20a%20thing%20we%20can%20do%20that%20will%20make%20us%20all%20better%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20its%20first%20year%2C%20Zhu%20said%20the%20club%20had%2020%20people%20who%20collectively%20earned%20an%20average%20monthly%20income%20of%20about%20%243%2C400.%20As%20of%20May%2C%20the%20club%20has%2050%20members%20and%20continues%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22589c43eb-39ed-4536-9ca9-28b195a42f7a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20basic%20income%20movement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Graphic%20showing%20money%20and%20expenses%20popping%20out%20of%20an%20envelope%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1cd3dcb4fb977f359829ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBasic%20incomes%20provide%20recurring%20cash%20payments%2C%20no%20strings%20attached.%3Cp%3EBurke%2FTriolo%20Productions%2FGetty%2C%5Ctkertlis%2FGetty%2C%20Pablo631%2FGetty%2C%5CtJoyImage%2FGetty%2C%20Tyler%20Le%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20Americans%2C%20Zhu%20became%20familiar%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20basic%20income%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandrew-yang-ai-income-inequality-ubi-universal-basic-income-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAndrew%20Yang's%3C%2Fa%3E%202020%20presidential%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYang%2C%20a%20tech%20entrepreneur%2C%20raised%20eyebrows%20when%20he%20proclaimed%20that%2C%20if%20elected%2C%20his%20administration%20would%20provide%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-basic-income-ubi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Euniversal%20basic%20income%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20%241%2C000%20a%20month%20to%20every%20adult%20to%20spend%20however%20they%20want%2C%20a%20policy%20he%20called%20%26quot%3BThe%20Freedom%20Dividend.%26quot%3B%20Yang%20said%20it%20was%20necessary%20to%20support%20American%20workers%20threatened%20by%20automation%20and%20inequality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20universal%20basic%20income%2C%20or%20some%20version%20of%20it%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-basic-income-ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehas%20gained%20momentum%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20AI%20threatens%20to%20remake%20the%20workforce.%20Musk%2C%20the%20man%20behind%20DOGE%2C%20supports%20what%20he%20calls%20a%20%26quot%3Buniversal%20high%20income.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUniversal%20high%20income%20via%20checks%20issued%20by%20the%20federal%20government%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20deal%20with%20unemployment%20caused%20by%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20billionaire%20CEO%20wrote%20on%20X%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20universal%20basic%20income%20provides%20monthly%20payments%20to%20an%20entire%20population%2C%20a%20guaranteed%20basic%20income%20typically%20provides%20unconditional%2C%20recurring%20cash%20payments%20to%20those%20who%20meet%20income%20thresholds%20or%20who%20belong%20to%20vulnerable%20social%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20cities%20and%20counties%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-basic-income-united-states%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeven%20some%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20experimented%20with%20these%20kinds%20of%20programs.%20In%20Baltimore%2C%20for%20example%2C%20a%20basic%20income%20program%20gave%20200%20struggling%20young%20parents%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguaranteed-universal-basic-income-ubi-baltimore-young-families-success-fund-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%241%2C000%20a%20month%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0no%20strings%20attached%2C%20between%202022%20and%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20programs%20have%20largely%20stayed%20small%2C%20however%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-basic-income-politics%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20political%20will%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20introduce%20statewide%20or%20even%20federal%20basic%20income%20programs%20remains%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20without%20a%20government%20behind%20them%2C%20the%20members%20of%20Zhu's%20club%20just%20rely%20on%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227cc7b0f2-c234-4c0b-ad13-13b79a3323a2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Giving%20is%20a%20muscle'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EZhu%20said%20the%20program's%20first%20year%20was%20largely%20successful.%20For%20one%2C%20he%20said%20some%20people%20who%20were%20initially%20unemployed%20and%20then%20found%20jobs%20stayed%20in%20the%20club%20to%20help%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20he%20said%2C%20there%20were%20club%20members%20who%20no%20longer%20had%20to%20worry%20about%20how%20they%20would%20buy%20groceries%20or%20medicine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20they%20knew%20that%20they%20had%20this%20community%20that%20was%20supporting%20them%2C%20they%20could%20go%20out%20and%20have%20more%20joy%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhu%20said.%20%26quot%3BGiving%20is%20a%20muscle%2C%20right%3F%20The%20more%20that%20you%20do%20it%2C%20the%20better%20you%20get%20at%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20building%20that%20muscle%20comes%20from%20maintaining%20community%2C%20something%20Zhu%20said%20can%20take%20time.%20He's%20begun%20hosting%20monthly%20social%20meetups%20for%20residents%20and%20has%20made%20an%20effort%20to%20welcome%20anyone%20interested%20in%20joining.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20hardest%20part%20of%20this%20is%20the%20relational%20aspect%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhu%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20way%20that%20we%20get%20people%20to%20join%20is%20mostly%20from%20trusted%20relationships.%20Hopefully%2C%20we%20can%20get%20to%20that%20point%20where%20we're%20bringing%20people%20in%20from%20completely%20different%20circles%2C%20but%20the%20trust%20is%20a%20big%20part%2C%20and%20the%20community%20aspect%20is%20important.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22037ca67d-a9e4-4d12-a8b3-d7dd7cfec7aa%5C%22%3ENeighbors%20helping%20neighbors%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20also%20some%20obstacles%20Zhu%20faced%20during%20the%20first%20year%2C%20including%20miscommunication%20about%20where%20to%20send%20money%2C%20missed%20payments%2C%20and%20a%20hesitance%20among%20some%20participants%20to%20ask%20for%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20other%20thing%20that%20I%20think%20like%20a%20lot%20of%20groups%20like%20this%20would%20face%20is%20that%20there%20will%20be%20an%20imbalance%20with%20the%20number%20of%20people%20who%20want%20to%20give%20and%20the%20number%20of%20people%20who%20need%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Zhu%20said%20it's%20important%20for%20people%20to%20step%20up%20and%20help%20their%20neighbors%2C%20especially%20when%20there's%20no%20government%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20love%20for%20it%20to%20be%20a%20thing%20that%20exists%20in%20the%20state%20or%20federal%20government%2C%20but%20until%20then%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20do%20it%20this%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20aiming%20to%20grow%20the%20Baltimore%20Community%20Guaranteed%20Income%20Club%20from%2050%20members%20to%20150%20members%20and%20expand%20its%20digital%20footprint%20with%20an%20official%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20those%20who%20say%20that%20it%20isn't%20going%20to%20work%2C%20they're%20wrong%2