the%20job%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMacedo%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFollow%20the%2015%20Minute%20Rule.%20If%20you%20are%20stuck%2C%20spend%20at%20least%2015%20minutes%20trying%20to%20solve%20it%20yourself%E2%80%94%20document%20what%20you%20tried%2C%20what%20failed%2C%20and%20what%20you%20searched%20for.%20That%20way%2C%20when%20you%20do%20ask%20for%20help%2C%20you%20can%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BI've%20tried%20X%20and%20Y%2C%20and%20I%20think%20the%20issue%20is%20Z.%20Can%20you%20point%20me%20in%20the%20right%20direction%3F%26quot%3B%20This%20shows%20respect%20for%20your%20manager%2Fmentor's%20time%20and%20demonstrates%20your%20problem-solving%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlum%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETake%20a%20moment%20to%20process%20and%20assess%20the%20situation%20first.%20That%20small%20pause%20often%20makes%20your%20question%20sharper%20and%20the%20answer%20you%20get%20back%20more%20useful%2C%20while%20also%20showing%20consideration%20for%20your%20colleagues'%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBorst%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-banks-ai-strategy-jpmorgan-goldman-citi-bofa-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20AI%20Assistant%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20certainly%20a%20great%20first%20stop%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20substitute%20for%20turning%20to%20the%20person%20sitting%20next%20to%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPersky%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI'd%20also%20encourage%20you%20to%20reframe%20how%20you%20think%20about%20asking%20for%20help%3A%20it%20doesn't%20signal%20confusion%20or%20lack%20of%20understanding.%20It's%20a%20good%20way%20to%20solicit%20feedback%20from%20others%20and%20give%20you%20a%20more%20diverse%20perspective.%20It%20should%20be%20part%20of%20your%20daily%20routine%2C%20not%20a%20last%20resort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226ef3bcfa-1ec3-4581-a327-12f6c65435ce%5C%22%3EWhat's%20an%20experience%20in%20your%20city%20that%20interns%20shouldn't%20miss%20this%20summer