oth-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-1-1757075398-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FShe-Lost-Both-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-1-1757075398-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FShe-Lost-Both-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-1-1757075398-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FShe-Lost-Both-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-1-1757075398-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496975%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAfter%20losing%20both%20parents%20as%20a%20teenager%2C%20Rupam%20Sonali%20vowed%20to%20fulfil%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20dream.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20sister%2C%20Rupali%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20our%20mother%20passed%20away%2C%20it%20was%20a%20tense%20and%20uncertain%20period%20for%20us.%20As%20the%20elder%20sister%2C%20I%20felt%20responsible%2C%20but%20Roopam%20too%20carried%20herself%20with%20remarkable%20strength.%20Mum%20always%20told%20us%20to%20never%20lose%20hope%20and%20to%20find%20something%20positive%20even%20in%20the%20worst%20of%20times.%20Those%20words%20carried%20us%20through.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%2C%20I%20was%20pursuing%20nursing%20training.%20Financially%2C%20we%20survived%20with%20the%20small%20savings%20left%20by%20our%20parents%20and%20by%20renting%20out%20a%20few%20rooms%20in%20the%20house.%20We%20were%20careful%20not%20to%20waste%20any%20amount%20from%20life%20insurance%20because%20we%20knew%20once%20that%20money%20was%20gone%2C%20it%20would%20never%20return%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2025-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERupam%20too%20refused%20to%20compromise%20on%20her%20studies.%20%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20very%20early%20that%20financial%20independence%20is%20the%20only%20weapon%20for%20a%20girl%20in%20such%20a%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20fund%20her%20education%2C%20she%20began%20tutoring%20students%20from%20Class%202%20to%20Class%2011.%20Every%20day%2C%20she%20woke%20at%204%20am%20to%20study%2C%20then%20travelled%2080%20kilometres%20from%20Kunti%20to%20Ranchi%20for%20her%20college.%20By%20afternoon%2C%20she%20was%20back%20home%2C%20and%20from%204%20pm%20to%207%20pm%2C%20she%20taught%20neighbourhood%20children.%20Only%20after%20dinner%20would%20she%20return%20to%20her%20books%2C%20often%20studying%20late%20into%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20study%20six%20to%20eight%20hours%20daily%2C%20mostly%20at%20dawn%20and%20late%20at%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rupam%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20lockdown%20years%20were%20actually%20a%20blessing%20because%20I%20could%20save%20travel%20time%20and%20focus%20completely%20on%20strengthening%20my%20base.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20journey%20was%20far%20from%20smooth.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F495179%2Fsubhankar-bala-ias-cleared-upsc-cse-without-coaching-delhi-shares-strategy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWithout%20coaching%20or%20mentors%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Rupam%20often%20doubted%20herself.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20times%20I%20thought%2C%20am%20I%20even%20studying%20the%20right%20way%3F%20Am%20I%20wasting%20my%20time%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20constant%20self-doubt.%20But%20every%20time%20I%20felt%20like%20giving%20up%2C%20my%20mother%E2%80%99s%20face%20on%20her%20deathbed%20came%20before%20me.%20That%20image%20would%20pull%20me%20back.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F