s%20of%20joy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20day%2C%20Rupali%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20overwhelming%20%E2%80%94%20tears%2C%20laughter%2C%20disbelief%20all%20at%20once.%20For%20me%2C%20her%20success%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20clearing%20an%20exam%3B%20it%20was%20proof%20that%20all%20the%20sacrifices%2C%20all%20the%20hardships%2C%20and%20the%20lessons%20our%20mother%20had%20instilled%20in%20us%20had%20carried%20us%20through.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COf%20course%2C%20not%20everyone%20reacted%20the%20same.%20Some%20people%20celebrated%2C%20while%20others%20compared%2C%20saying%20she%20was%20lucky%2C%20their%20child%20wasn%E2%80%99t.%20But%20I%20believe%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20balance%20of%20fate%20and%20hard%20work.%20Roopam%20worked%20tirelessly%2C%20and%20destiny%20met%20her%20halfway%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Rupali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FShe-Lost-Both-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-3-1757075513.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%2022%2C%20Rupam%20cleared%20JPSC%20in%20her%20first%20attempt%2C%20without%20coaching%20and%20against%20all%20odds.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FShe-Lost-Both-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-3-1757075513.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FShe-Lost-Both-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-3-1757075513-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FShe-Lost-Both-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-3-1757075513-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia